    "/wallet/amount-locks": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Amount Locks"
        ],
        "summary": "Get amount locks",
        "description": "\u26a0\ufe0f Balance that can be withdrawn depends on the sum of amounts locks across all currencies.\n\n\u2139\ufe0f Locked amount is not visible as a fraction of reserved balance.\n\n**Permission**: Withdraw cryptocurrencies\n\n**IP limit**: 10/10\n\n**Account limit**: 20/30\n",
