        "description": "\u26a0\ufe0f Activation is applicable if the only reason a subaccount has `\"disable\"` status is it was frozen. If there are other reasons underlying the status change, rolling back it is beyond control of the super account.\n\n**Permission**: None\n\n**Account limit**: 20/30\n",
